[For those who may not be able to access the graph, it shows that the peak
of cases during years 1995/96 occurred between weeks 29 and 43. During
1997 the peak occurred between weeks 37 and 47, and in 1998 the peak had
not yet been reached by week 44. - Mod.ES]
